reviewText: Three good Marky Mark movies. ( not a fan of the rockstar one) happy with the purchase for the price.

Although we have collected all 4 movies in single showing format, we were searching for a few movies for back-to-back viewing on movie nights. All 4 films are pretty good, and 'The Perfect Storm' is our old-time favorite. It's the kind of movie you can watch over-and-over, and Not get bored.

These movies are filled with drama & entertain from start to finish. 'The Perfect Storm' includes action, Special Effects are awesome, and the entire cast gave a Superb acting performance. 4 entertaining films on movie night, along with a reasonable price. Enjoyable, and highly recommended!
can't get enough of marky mark!
Not the greatest that I have seen of his movies. We have a few others made later on in his career, example, Italian Job--super movie. He gets better as he gets older.
Four walberg movies for a low price. The only thing that would of made this even better is if one of the four movies was four brothers. Maybe that quadruple set is already available. Ha.
